Class BatteryObserver.AggregateBatteryClassification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer.BatteryObserver.AggregateBatteryClassification

    BatteryObserver

    @Immutable
protected static final class BatteryObserver.AggregateBatteryClassification
extends java.lang.Object
    POJO for tracking BatteryLevelEvent.BatteryStateClassification for both mobile and wearable device types, to be used as this Observer's observable type.
